abstract: The warning signaled that the price war between A.M.D. and its main rival, Intel, had taken its toll.
snippet: The warning signaled that the price war between A.M.D. and its main rival, Intel, had taken its toll.
lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO, Jan. 12  In the turf war that has come to characterize the computer chip market, Advanced Micro Devices, appears to have stumbled in the fourth quarter.

headline.main: A.M.D., in Price War With Intel, Warns of Disappointing Revenue
headline.print_headline: A.M.D., in Price War With Intel, Warns of Disappointing Revenue
